Hey everyone - hope you're all doing well! It's a research week for me again this week, which means I'm busy preparing the next block of videos I'm about to share with you all. But like I said before, instead of missing an upload I've put together a compilation of previous videos so at least I still have something to share with you guys!

And don’t worry, these will never replace my normal uploads, you’ll still be getting exactly the same number of new uploads as you normally do throughout the year!! It just means I’ll have something to upload whenever I take a week off for research, so this way a video every week is guaranteed 😊

Hope you enjoy the rest of your weekend!
